Folder and files description


default
  contain default data, those data shared be each site.
  now it is copy from spree/core/db/default/spree/*.rb
firstshop
  user access a site, actually a page to apply shop information,
  for now, we just load the first shop for that purpose.
sample
  while user apply for new online shop, he could decide wether load sample data as well.
  this folder contain all sample data. copied from spree/sample/db/sample, we would customize it for china. 
seeds.rb

  task 'rake db:seed' would load this file to load seeds.

  